trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] An <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint> maintains two ActivityTrackingLocationCollection objects: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A> specifies parameters used for matching activity status events and <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A> specifies parameters used to exclude activity status events from matching.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Um <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>mantém dois objetos ActivityTrackingLocationCollection: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A>Especifica os parâmetros usados para eventos de status de atividade de correspondência e <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A>Especifica os parâmetros usados para excluir eventos de status de atividade de correspondência.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>

trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocationCollection"> </xref> classe usando uma lista de locais de atividade.
